Cc: blitz-list@helsinki.fi
Subject: Re: your mail

> 
> Its the Open_'s command accessMode parameter that im stuck with.  I assume
> accessMode is either read or write, but is it expecting a number, string
> or what?
> 
> Thanx for any help.
 Paul:
#MODE_OLDFILE   =  1005 ;open existing file read/write.
#MODE_NEWFILE   =  1006 ;open freshly created file (delete old 
                        ;file) read/write.
#MODE_READWRITE =  1004 ;open old file with shared lock, 
                        ;creates file it if doesn't exist.
                        
GREETINGS !!!
  Pedro.



