From sueec@westminster.ac.ukSun Sep  3 22:30:16 1995
Date: Fri, 2 Jun 1995 14:58:13 +0100 (BST)
From: Ricky Clarke <sueec@westminster.ac.uk>
To: blitz-list@helsinki.fi
