-----------------------------Schnipp-----------------------------------

DEFTYPE .Locale *myloc
DEFTYPE .Catalog *mycat



If OpenLibrary_ ("locale.library",38)
  bi$="deutsch"+Chr$(0)
  wtag$+Mkl$($80090001) +  Mkl$(&bi$)
  wtag$+ Mkl$(0) +Mkl$(0)
  *mycat=OpenCatalogA_ (0,"pgptogui.catalog",&wtag$)
  CloseCatalog_ (*mycat)
End If

a$="Default Text"

Print Peek$ (GetCatalogStr_(*mycat,2,&a$))

----------------------------Schnapp--------------------------------------

Even if i write "STOP" in the very first line, BB2 attemps to load the
locale.library. (Says Snoopdos)

I get crazy ! *Please* help me !!!

Many thanks....



