From mmmakela@cc.helsinki.fiSun Sep  3 22:30:25 1995
Date: Thu, 24 Aug 1995 15:14:46 +0300 (EETDST)
From: Mikko Makela <mmmakela@cc.helsinki.fi>
To: blitz-list@helsinki.fi
Subject: comp.sys.amiga.programmer anyone? (fwd)

Forwarded message:

> From: acid@iconz.co.nz (Simon Armstrong)
> Subject: comp.sys.amiga.programmer anyone?
> 
