From phips@scout.rhein-main.deSun Sep  3 22:30:26 1995
Date: Thu, 24 Aug 95 18:56:36 CET
From: Philipp Lonke <phips@scout.rhein-main.de>
To: blitz-list@helsinki.fi
Subject: Re: Cycling Gadget...

Hi Josh, you wrote in <s039d189.065@GWSMTP.WILTEL.COM> on Aug 22:

> Is there some sample code for using a cycling gadget, somewhere?  It
> doesn't seem that cycling gadgets are directly supported in Blitz (at least
> not the version I have), and I wanted to make sure... Thanks.

either you use the blitz gadgets with

 TextGadget a,b,c,d,e,"This|Will|Cycle"

or you use GadTools (avaiable at least in BB2 v1.9)

 GTCycle list,id,x,y,w,h,"This|Cycles|Better",flags,options

or you use Triton

 !CycleGadget{&cycles(1),id,top}


