sense of a Cycle gadget that walks through the window moved by e.g.
the cursor keys?? Or did you mean to change the visible cycle entry??
This is no problem and easily to change!

> > Resizing the window or anything else concerning the layout is no more
> > your task and/or problem - TRITON will do it for you.
> 
